  @invariant  ec owns caret/selection/clipboard; no MIDI state — mutations go via tm/cm  @ 5
  @invariant  selection = anchor (fixed) + cursor (moving); sel is the resolved rect  @ 6
  @invariant  sel == nil iff no selection  @ 7
  @invariant  region()'s cursor-degenerate fallback is callsite policy, not stored  @ 8
  @invariant  hBlockScope ∈ {0=free, 1=col, 2=channel, 3=all-cols}  @ 9
  @invariant  vBlockScope ∈ {0=free, 1=beat, 2=bar×vBlockBars, 3=all-rows}; scopes are orthogonal  @ 10
  @invariant  sticky == any nonzero scope; moves under sticky update sel, never clear  @ 11
  @invariant  hBlock=2/3 use part1=part2='*'; selectionStopSpan falls through to whole-col  @ 12
  @invariant  parts within a col order by col.partStart, not stop (parts may be multi-stop)  @ 13
  @invariant  moveHook fires after every position change (paired with clampPos)  @ 14
  @invariant  sel.part1/part2 are part names, or '*' sentinel under hBlock=2/3  @ 16
  @invariant  clip.single.type ∈ {'note', '7bit', 'pb'}  @ 19

